designer on my chest.\", \"from\": 715, \"to\": 826, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everybody\", \"from\": 727, \"to\": 736}, {\"ngram\": \"a black designer\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 813}, {\"ngram\": \"my chest\", \"from\": 817, \"to\": 825}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is what I stand for, and I am making a way for everybody in my position.\\\"\", \"from\": 827, \"to\": 905, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 874}, {\"ngram\": \"everybody\", \"from\": 879, \"to\": 888}, {\"ngram\": \"my position\", \"from\": 892, \"to\": 903}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'If you know me then you know EXACTLY what I meant by my speech.\", \"from\": 909, \"to\": 973, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my speech\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 972}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you do not, it wasn't for you & that is OK!'\", \"from\": 974, \"to\": 1021, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Elder'sreaction?\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1039, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Elder'sreaction\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1038}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Alaysha 'Lay' Johnson (@ImJustLaylay), congrats on making the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1040, \"to\": 1112, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1055, \"end\": 1062, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Johnson\", \"score\": 0.515149012306216, \"rank\": 0.7080305926390855, \"text\": \"Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Johnson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Johnson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1099, \"to\": 1111}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But why the, 'This is for everybody who [sic] looks like me' crap?\", \"from\": 1113, \"to\": 1179, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everybody\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1148}, {\"ngram\": \"me' crap\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1178}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was but ONE non-black runner - and she finished next to last.\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1247, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ONE non-black runner\", \"from\": 1194, \"to\": 1214}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Can we quit this 'we shall overcome' BS?\", \"from\": 1248, \"to\": 1288, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"BS\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1287}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For crying out loud, this is 2024!\\\"\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1324, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The post from Elder - who has 1.5 million followers on X - has attracted about 50,000 likes since it went live Sunday and has garnered over 2,000 comments.\", \"from\": 1328, \"to\": 1483, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The post\", \"from\": 1328, \"to\": 1336}, {\"ngram\": \"Elder\", \"from\": 1342, \"to\": 1347}, {\"ngram\": \"1.5 million followers\", \"from\": 1358, \"to\": 1379}, {\"ngram\": \"X\", \"from\": 1383, \"to\": 1384}, {\"ngram\": \"about 50,000 likes\", \"from\": 1401, \"to\": 1419}, {\"ngram\": \"over 2,000 comments\", \"from\": 1463, \"to\": 1482}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here are a few of them: The day after the race, Johnson posted the following message onX: \\\"If you know me then you know EXACTLY what I meant by my speech.\", \"from\": 1484, \"to\": 1639, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1533, \"end\": 1540, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Johnson\", \"score\": 0.515149012306216, \"rank\": 0.7080305926390855, \"text\": \"Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Johnson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Johnson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1530}, {\"ngram\": \"the following message\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1568}, {\"ngram\": \"onX\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1572}, {\"ngram\": \"my speech\", \"from\": 1628, \"to\": 1637}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you do not, it wasn't for you & that is OK!\\\"\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1687, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Johnson's personal-best 12.31 in the finals put her a hair behind winner Masai Russell's 12.25,USA Today reported, adding that Russell's time broke Gail Devers' 24-year-old meet record and was the fastest time in the world this year.\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1922, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1762, \"end\": 1767, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maasai_people\", \"score\": 0.9999999957176442, \"rank\": 4.282352982982708e-09, \"text\": \"Masai\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maasai_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maasai_people\"}, {\"begin\": 1768, \"end\": 1775, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\", \"score\": 0.9999659077500251, \"rank\": 2.4489682869408116e-05, \"text\": \"Russell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q4964182\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\"}, {\"begin\": 1816, \"end\": 1823, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\", \"score\": 0.9999659077500251, \"rank\": 2.4489682869408116e-05, \"text\": \"Russell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q4964182\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\"}, {\"begin\": 1837, \"end\": 1848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gail_Devers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gail Devers\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gail_Devers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gail_Devers\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the finals\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1732}, {\"ngram\": \"a hair\", \"from\": 1741, \"to\": 1747}, {\"ngram\": \"the fastest time\", \"from\": 1882, \"to\": 1898}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1902, \"to\": 1911}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"People like me who come from the inner city of Houston ... it's hard for us to get opportunities,\\\" Johnson - a 27-year-old who ran at the University of Oregon and Texas Tech -told the Associated Press.\", \"from\": 1924, \"to\": 2126, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1972, \"end\": 1979, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\", \"score\": 0.9991337841482519, \"rank\": 0.0006065720262599744, \"text\": \"Houston\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\"}, {\"begin\": 2088, \"end\": 2098, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas_Tech_Red_Raiders\", \"score\": 0.6528640972198135, \"rank\": 0.30311506370140084, \"text\": \"Texas Tech\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas_Tech_Red_Raiders\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas_Tech_Red_Raiders\"}, {\"begin\": 2109, \"end\": 2125, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999822492770578, \"rank\": 1.775091473578478e-05, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the inner city\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 1968}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1998, \"to\": 2000}, {\"ngram\": \"opportunities\", \"from\": 2008, \"to\": 2021}, {\"ngram\": \"the University\", \"from\": 2059, \"to\": 2073}, {\"ngram\": \"Oregon\", \"from\": 2077, \"to\": 2083}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It always takes what I say is double the effort to get half as far.\", \"from\": 2127, \"to\": 2195, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the effort\", \"from\": 2165, \"to\": 2175}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I always tell people if we had a little bit more support, I probably could have been here a long time ago.\", \"from\": 2196, \"to\": 2302, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2210, \"to\": 2216}, {\"ngram\": \"a little bit more support\", \"from\": 2227, \"to\": 2252}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it made me understand that regardless of how many people have your back, I am still strong enough to do this on my own two feet.\\\"\", \"from\": 2303, \"to\": 2436, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"how many people\", \"from\": 2348, \"to\": 2363}, {\"ngram\": \"your back\", \"from\": 2369, \"to\": 2378}, {\"ngram\": \"my own two feet\", \"from\": 2419, \"to\": 2434}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Johnson has hypothyroidism, which causes fatigue, and she told the outlet she cut back on her warm-up Sunday \\\"to make sure I can conserve as much as I could to be able to get through 10 hurdles.\\\"\", \"from\": 2438, \"to\": 2633, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2438, \"end\": 2445, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Johnson\", \"score\": 0.515149012306216, \"rank\": 0.7080305926390855, \"text\": \"Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Johnson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Johnson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hypothyroidism\", \"from\": 2450, \"to\": 2464}, {\"ngram\": \"fatigue\", \"from\": 2479, \"to\": 2486}, {\"ngram\": \"the outlet\", \"from\": 2501, \"to\": 2511}, {\"ngram\": \"her warm-up Sunday\", \"from\": 2528, \"to\": 2546}, {\"ngram\": \"10 hurdles\", \"from\": 2621, \"to\": 2631}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The AP added that Johnson also ran on borrowed spikes after the \\\"bubble popped\\\" on the only pair she took with her to the trials.\", \"from\": 2634, \"to\": 2763, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2638, \"end\": 2640, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999999824347016, \"rank\": 1.7563324418031595e-08, \"text\": 